### Welcome to Bootstrap-outline-btn.
This might (actually its very likely) already be out in the world but I found myself copying my own code and going and finding stuff out on the internet. So I just threw the good stuff for this functionality into a file and I will keep it here. Its very simple here it is.

```

.btn-outline {
    color: inherit;
    background-color: transparent;
}

.btn-primary.btn-outline {
    color: #428bca;
}

```


